<LP>
   BANK OF TOKYO Ltd. -- The bank named Keishi Fujii, 51
years old, president of Bank of Tokyo Trust Co. N.Y., a U.S.
subsidiary. The Tokyo-based bank also said it expects to name
Mr. Fujii a director of the parent. Mr. Fujii, previously
general manager of the corporate advisory division at the
parent, succeeds Hiroshi Hayashi, 53, who assumes a new post
at Tokyo headquarters.
