<LP>
   ESTEE LAUDER Cos. (New York) -- The closely held cosmetics
company's Estee Lauder U.S.A. unit appointed Robert J. Luzzi,
37 years old, who owns a design company here, to the new
position of senior vice president of creative design. Mr.
Luzzi will report to Robin Burns, president and chief
executive officer of the Lauder subsidiary.
