<HL>
   Business Brief -- HQ Office Supplies Warehouse:
   Chain Completes Public Sale
   For an Initial $8.6 Million
</HL>
<DATE>
06/19/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   HQOSA
</CO>
<IN>
STOCK MARKET, OFFERINGS (STK)
BOND MARKET NEWS (BON)
</IN>
<LP>
   HQ Office Supplies Warehouse Inc., Long Beach, Calif.,
said it completed a public offering of 10,000 units of
securities, providing initial net proceeds of $8.6 million.
   The operator of office supply stores said it will use
proceeds to open three new stores this summer, to pay debt
and for working capital.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Each unit consists of $1,000 principal amount of
convertible subordinated debentures due June 1, 1995, and 200
Class C warrants to purchase 200 Class A common shares. The
units were priced at $1,000 each.
</TEXT>
