   PUBLISHING: The senior executives of Chicago magazine
formed a new company with Landmark Communications Inc. that
will acquire the stake in the monthly held by Adams
Communications Inc. Terms, including the specific stake Adams
holds, weren't disclosed.
                                                                                                       

</LP>
<TEXT>
   WHO'S NEWS: Andrew Susskind was named president of Imagine
Films Entertainment Inc.'s Imagine Television unit. He was
president of the television division of Weintraub
Entertainment Group Inc. He assumes some duties of Robert A.
Harris, who left to become an independent producer. Brian
Grazer and Ron Howard, co-chairmen of Imagine Films
Entertainment, have assumed Mr. Harris's former duties for
motion pictures.
