<LP>
   Mitsubishi Corp. said it is considering setting up a
joint-venture company with Chrysler Corp. in Ontario to
produce medium-sized passenger cars, but the Japanese trading
company emphasized that no decisions have been made.
   A Mitsubishi spokesman said the proposed venture, which
has been under discussion for the past year, would be in
